- rch/src/commands.rs - Command implementations (10k+ lines)

## Design Principles
1. **Consistency**: Same flags should work the same way across all commands
2. **Safety**: Destructive/disruptive operations need confirmation
3. **Discoverability**: Related functionality should be grouped logically
4. **Efficiency**: Common operations should have short forms

